The paper discusses the use of advanced concepts such as neural networks, recommender engines, and reinforcement learning to improve the quality of retail banking services. These concepts are commonly studied in the computer science sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computer engineering (cs.CE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
